@prefix yse: <https://github.com/tykimos/onto-osint-yuseong-event/ontology#> .
@prefix yseo: <https://github.com/tykimos/onto-osint-yuseong-event/ontology/class#> .
@prefix yser: <https://github.com/tykimos/onto-osint-yuseong-event/ontology/relation#> .
